title: What a Mess! # 1011 (Ep 1011)
description:
In this episode I break down the top takeaways from the Democrat debate. I also address troubling new revelations about this key Obama administration official’s role in Spygate. Finally, I address another big tech company suppressing conservative content. News Picks:Another bombshell Spygate piece from John Solomon.



A landmine was laid for Elizabeth Warren last night.



Winners and losers from last night’s Dem debate.



Trump hilariously mocks NBC for their technical meltdown during the debate.



Now Reddit is censoring Trump supporters.



Nice job liberals, you even ruined the World Cup.
